In this video, I set out to find the best pizza in New York 🍕🇺🇸 With the help of my friend @yosebby a New Yorker who knows his pizza (and just lost his favourite spot 😢 Joanne's Gourmet Pizza - 1067 Northern Blvd, Roslyn, NY, if anyone knows them please get in touch would love to arrange for Seb to try Joanne’s one more time).
We hit up 8 pizza places in Manhattan, 2 in Long Island, and 1 in Brooklyn to find his new go-to slice. We rate each spot, take the average of our scores, and crown the ultimate NYC pizza champion. Which spot takes the top spot? Watch to find out!
